chat.msg: hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
si
guay! ahora mismo estoy en el punto de partida mirando el mapa
veo un montón de cosas, como una isla pequeña con un tigre a la izquierda. ¿para dónde debo ir primero?
hacia la isla con el tigre
perfecto, aquí estamos, en la isla del tigre
¿dónde debo ir después? ¿hacia la isla de la mariposa al sureste o la del loro al suroeste?
no a la isla con el el pajaro
de acuerdo, estoy siguiendo tu consejo y me dirijo a la isla del loro
aquí estoy ahora. ¿qué sigue a continuación?
pero pasate sobre el
hecho, he cruzado sobre el loro
estoy mirando a unas rocas que llevan a una isla con una rana. ¿pasamos por ahí?
si y vete un poco mas hacia la derecha de la rana,despues regresate y cruza por el caiman a la rosca k llega a la isla con el elefante
vale, seguí tus instrucciones y me moví un poco a la derecha de la rana, luego volví, crucé el caimán y llegué a la isla del elefante
despues cruzate a la isla con la girafa
ok, cruzado a la isla de la jirafa
aquí estamos. ¿y ahora qué?
cruza a la isla con la vivora
ok, he cruzado a la isla con la víbora
¡qué emocionante!
si, llegaste al tesoro
¡genial! he llegado al tesoro
eso fue divertido, gracias por la ayuda. *finished*
hola, you ready?
si
awesome! alright, first move a bit westward, towards that wooden bench but don't sit down yet! cross that trail and just before you reach the florist stand, pull a swift u-turn
ready to head back to our white furry friend now?
yes
great! now cross over that branch and head straight south
you'll see another white dog, chillin' by a checked picnic mat. isn't he cute?
yes, he is
good
let's keep going. step over the mat, don't step on the berries! then head west
and now
brace yourself! we're crossing a river
see that wooden branch nearby? use it to get to the other side, heading north
and now where do i go?
now, spot that green bush? walk right to it, but go around it from the right side
don't touch it, just circle it! you'll arrive at the florist stand. neat, ain't it?
yes!
good stuff! now just turn left (west), slip under that stand, and voila! there’s a bridge
see the cyclists on it? we're headed in their direction
ok
now keep strolling westward, we're passing this cool bridge! enjoying the view?
we are
ponder this! right after the bridge, you'll see two elderly folks, just taking it easy, enjoying the day
isn't life grand?
it is. where to now?
now, just step a bit south
do you see a wooden branch and a bush? we are heading towards them
ok
nice! now go east between the branch and the bush
hi there, empezamos?
si
alright! i'm at the tent up north
where to from here?
head south past the dog toward the trail
passed the dog now
should i go towards the red mushroom or the fire?
head east towards the fire, but go around the top of the fire then back down toward the trail before you get to the car
aight, gone around the fire, now on the path before the car
following the trailing head south toward the telescope, then pass between the telescope and the bush immediately to its right
got it, i'm past the telescope and the bush now
i see some rocks and a house nearby. what's next?
head west toward the house, then pass in the gap in the rocks to your north towards the hosue
cool, i'm now at the house
*finished*! that was fun!
hola, q tal? ready to play?
si
¡perfecto! let's start at the three palm trees
go southwest under the first tree, make a right at the second tree, then a quick left before the third one. heads up, we're heading south!
ok
i see a cute brown puppy ahead
veer to its left, then make a gentle left and go right straight to the south. onwards!
then wehre
look for a big rock on your left and a small rock on your right
walk between them straight to the ocean, mate!
ok then towards the crab?
you got it! face the crab, then veer right along the rock
let's keep moving in the ocean westward
how far
just until you're parallel with a medium-sized rock on your right
cool stuff ahead!
ok
so there's this shark, right? well
make a sharp right when you see it!
to the ball
back on land first, then yes! go between the rock and the soccer ball
head north after that!
after that?
veer slightly left and head towards the red tent and a big speaker
where to then?
circle the tent, then head south, but stop before the water
ok
turn right, see that red kayak? go underneath it! go west, my friend!
ok
next, turn right again, walk along the kayak until you reach a small green bush
you’ve made it! well done, mate!
